  <brief_title>Predicting Normal vs. Carrier Status in Euploid Embryos of Translocation Carriers</brief_title>
  <official_title>Evaluation of the Accuracy of Predicting Normal or Carrier Status in Euploid Embryos Produced by Patients With Balanced Translocations</official_title>
  <sponsors>
